data.description: Come explore this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3.5-bath residence on Amelia Island, located within the prestigious Dunes of Amelia community. Originally the "MODEL" home, this immaculate property built in 2018 offers an unparalleled blend of luxury, comfort, and picturesque water vistas from both levels. Enjoy a thoughtfully designed open floor plan with a bonus room that can easily serve as an office, providing versatility and comfort for modern living. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring quartz countertops, a gas stove top, and high-end appliances, making meal preparation a breeze. Gorgeous wood-like tile floors span the main living areas, combining aesthetics with durability. The first-floor owner's suite is a sanctuary, offering breathtaking water views, a luxurious soaking tub, an oversized dual shower, and a generously sized custom wood closet. Step onto the covered porch accessible from the great room and kitchen. Located just minutes from the beaches of Amelia Island
